values:
Name your top 10 most played bands on Last.fm:
1 The Sounds 498
2 The Strokes 316
3 Muse 232
4 The Rakes 196
5 Panic! at the Disco 181
6 The Killers 169
7 She Wants Revenge 165
8 Patrick Wolf 160
9 White Rose Movement 155
10 My Chemical Romance 154

<lj-cut text="Now answer the questions according to the numbers:">
// what was the first song you ever heard by 6?
Somebody Told Me

// what is your favourite album of 2?
First Impressions of Earth

// what is your favourite lyric that 5 has sung?
That first verse of Lying is the Most Fun. I won't quote it, it's too long.

// how many times have you seen 4 live?
None.

// what is your favourite song by 7?
Monologue and Someone Must Get Hurt.

// what is a good memory you have considering the music of 10?
Hating the music of number 10.

// is there a song of 3 that makes you sad?
No.

// what is your favourite lyric that 2 has sung?
Take me away
See I've got to explain
Things, they have changed
In such a permanent way
Life seems unreal
Can we go back to your place?
Oh, "You drink too much"
Makes me drink just the same


// what is your favourite song by 9?
Speed.

// how did you get in to 3?
I think I was just downloading random songs out of a music community, trying to find a new band to listen to. I found one!

// what was the first song you heard by 1?
Mine for Life, I think. Or Dance with Me.

// what is your favourite song by 4?
iProblem.

// how many time have you seen 9 live?
None.

// what is a good memory you have concerning 2?
When Nick Valensi was the prettiest man I could think of.

// is there a song of 8 that makes you sad?
Yeah, that part in Wind in the Wires about birds. Actually, both parts about birds.

// what is your favourite album of 5?
That one they have.

// what is your favourite lyric that 3 has sung?
Everything about you is how I'd wanna be
Your freedom comes naturally
Everything about you resonates happiness
Now i won't settle for less
Give me
All the peace and joy in your mind
Everything about you pains my envying
Your soul can't hate anything
Everything about you is so easy to love
They're watching you from above

// what is your favourite song of 1?
Don't Want to Hurt You, Living in America, Painted by Numbers, Ego, Dance With Me, all of them really.

// what is your favourite song of 10?
To the End. I guess. Eh?

// how many times have you seen 8 live?
None.

// what is your favourite album of 1?
Ooh umm. I can't decide. They're both too great.

// what is a great memory you have considering 9?
Misinterpretation of lyrics. Crack! Wet crack!

// what was the first song you heard by 8?
Either To the Lighthouse or The Libertine, probably.</lj-cut>

I'm seeing the Strokes in only 3(ish) days. It hasn't really hit me yet. I'm only sort of...mildly happy about it. I'm actually terrified that I'm going to forget the tickets.
